name: skymansionx/AI-Art-Generator
description: 🎨 AI Art Generator: A project using generative models (GANs, Diffusion) to create images from text prompts. 🤖 Explores the intersection of AI and creativity. 🖼️

name: skymansionx/Pong-Remake
description: 🕹️ Retro Gaming Project: A precise, physics-based remake of Pong. 🎾 Focuses on robust multiplayer logic and advanced collision detection algorithms. A coding challenge! 🏆

description: 👹 Roguelike Dungeon Crawler: A classic turn-based roguelike game with procedurally generated levels. 🗺️ Features permadeath and challenging gameplay. ⚔️

description: 📤 Secure-Upload-Service: A File Uploader Tool that handles secure file storage, management, and sharing with user authentication. Focuses on cloud integration. 🌐

name: skymansionx/Code-Dependency-Visualizer
description: 🕸️ Code Dependency Visualizer: A tool that parses a codebase and generates a visual graph of its dependencies. 🗺️ Helps understand complex project structures. 📊

name: skymansionx/StockTrack-Portfolio
description: 💰 Finance Portfolio Tracker: A StockTrack tool offering real-time stock market data visualization. 📈 Tracks comprehensive portfolio valuation. API integration required. 💸 📉

name: skymansionx/Geography-Quiz-Game
description: 🌎 Geography Quiz Game: A geographical quiz testing knowledge of countries and capitals. ❓ Includes flags and famous landmarks through interactive questioning. Educational and engaging. 🗺️ 📚

name: skymansionx/JobBoard-Finder
description: 📋 Job Board Finder: A simple job board platform for posting and searching job listings. 🔎 Filter listings based on salary, location, and required skills. 👤 💼

name: skymansionx/Vision-Detection-API
description: 🚗 Vision-Detection-API: A project that uses a computer vision model (like YOLO) to detect objects in images or video streams. A great entry to practical AI. 💻

name: skymansionx/Voice-Command-System
description: 🎙️ Voice-Command-System: A custom skill or action for a voice assistant like Alexa or Google Assistant. A fun way to learn about voice-first user interfaces. 💡

name: skymansionx/Sudoku-Game-Solver

name: skymansionx/My-Library-App
description: 📚 My-Library App: An application for cataloging and tracking personal book libraries with advanced filtering and search functionality. Focuses on database normalization. 🔖
